durable, resumable, asynchronous file transfer
==============================================

frame:
    magic | version
    len
    cbor payload

start_req
    file tree:
        list of leaf dirs/perms
        list of files/perms

start_rep
    status (ok/error)
    session id
    file-id mapping

[idempotent]
chunk_req
    session id
    file id
    offset
    len
    [hash]

chunk_rep
    session id
    file id
    offset
    len

ping
    session id

pong
    session id

status_req
    session id

status_rep
    session id
    session start time
    session end time
    pct complete

